
/*======== Introduction ========*/

What is HTML Email: HTML Email is an open source build automation system for technology in the Java (JVM) world. Gradle adds to Ant and Maven concepts and uses a directed acyclic graph to determine execution order. Gradle provides a Groovy-based domain-specific language and was designed for multi-project scalable builds.

